{"title": "Joseph: Beloved, Hated, Exalted", "description": "I remember seeing the huge Matterhorn reflected, in its minutest details, in a small mountain lakelet, many miles distant; and similarly, the life of Jesus is remarkably mirrored in this touching story.  In fact, there are scenes in the life of Joseph which probably foreshadow events that are timed to happen in the near future, and which depict them with a vividness and minuteness not to be found elsewhere on the page of Scripture.  It is here only that we can fully realize what will take place when the Lord Jesus makes Himself known to his brethren according to the flesh, and they exclaim, \"It is Jesus our brother!\"  (From the Preface)", "duration": 19985, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "10499", "name": "Frederick Brotherton Meyer"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/librivoxcdcoverart34/joseph_1602.jpg", "copyright_year": "1910", "genres": ["Christianity - Commentary"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "DaveC"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Early Days", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/joseph_1602_librivox/joseph_01_meyer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1038}, {"section": 2, "title": "The Pit", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/joseph_1602_librivox/joseph_02_meyer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1204}, {"section": 3, "title": "In the House of Potiphar", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/joseph_1602_librivox/joseph_03_meyer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1527}, {"section": 4, "title": "The Secret of Purity", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/joseph_1602_librivox/joseph_04_meyer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 635}, {"section": 5, "title": "Misunderstood and Impriosoned", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/joseph_1602_libriv